<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-2492] add an escapeSQLString function and fix unescapeSQLString</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-2492</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;CliUtils.unescapeSqlString repeats the escape character e.g. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&quot;my \\t tab&quot; becomes &quot;my \tt&quot;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;because &lt;tt&gt;i&lt;/tt&gt; is not bumped when an escape is processed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also for Cassandra-2221 I need a function to escape strings back so they will work if processed by the cli again. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are a number of non &lt;a href=&quot;http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jls/second_edition/html/lexical.doc.html#101089&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;standard escapes&lt;/a&gt; which I assume is a hang over from is original source &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/1aeca2b6257b0ad6680080b1756edf7ee9acf8c8/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/cli/CliUtils.java&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/1aeca2b6257b0ad6680080b1756edf7ee9acf8c8/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/cli/CliUtils.java&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Will change to use the &lt;a href=&quot;http://commons.apache.org/lang/api-2.5/org/apache/commons/lang/StringEscapeUtils.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;StringEscapeUtils&lt;/a&gt; class  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
